{
  "epId": 1005,
  "name": "流明石觸媒",
  "desc": "「層岩巨淵·地下礦區」中裝備時，能夠提供光照的珍貴晶體。<br/><br/>在成分上與僅在層岩巨淵出產的琉璃晶砂有相當的共同之處，但其中含有更加濃烈的力量。<br/>但願它能如同掌心的小太陽一樣，為黑暗中的跋涉帶來些許光亮、些許慰藉。",
  "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/12/21/142453215/6d9b7de4c9664500df58a4252d5270bd_4899155244703511583.png",
  "filterValues": {
    "objectType": [
      "小道具"
    ]
  },
  "menuId": 9,
  "menuName": "提瓦特產物",
  "version": 1734967502,
  "components": {
    "customize": [
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "level": 1,
        "text": "教學",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/20/237301566/ace43fb68f3bb7ce7c20450ae8271318_6439520210675330086.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "裝備流明石觸媒時，若其中儲存有能量，就能夠提供光照。但是，或許是因為依賴特殊的地脈環境吧，流明石觸媒僅能在層岩巨淵·地下礦區生效。"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/20/237301566/fd50171c4d37d1fff816749628bfa74a_1384330742438288557.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "一些特定的機關、生物，如明石燈、吉光蟲，能補充觸媒的能量。"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/20/237301566/11d67bbebe35e627cea12edd834a16ee_8730455000715405422.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "或許勘探隊中有人能強化流明石觸媒的力量吧..."
      },
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "level": 1,
        "text": "流明石觸媒強化",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "每 <color=#ffffff>8</color> 個",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 3831,
        "name": "流明晶石",
        "desc": "<p>湛藍如天幕的晶石，表面光芒明滅，似乎在呼應著地層深處不可見的高遠天空...<br>側耳細聽，彷彿能聽到其中傳來細微的嘆息。<br>說來奇怪，這塊晶石有一種溫暖的觸感。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/125391187/c61ace426856fcf41defec2fc476720f_4686018313795104572.png",
        "displayStyle": "text",
        "menuId": 9
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "將強化 <color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 1等級。\n將 <color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 強化至等級2、等級6和等級8時，需要額外1個",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 1004,
        "name": "流明石原礦",
        "desc": "流明石的璞礦，稍加雕琢的話似乎可以用來增強手中的流明石「觸媒」，不如去找瑾武諮詢看看…",
        "iconUrl": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/object/Lumenstone Ore_icon.png",
        "displayStyle": "text",
        "menuId": 9
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "。\n<color=#ffffff>等級</color>\n<color=#ffffff>強化效果</color>\n1",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 能儲存的能量上限提升至 <color=#ffffff>3</color> 單位。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "2",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "主動使用 <color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 時，將進行 <color=#ffe14b>純光綻放</color> ：消耗儲存的能量釋放光芒，破壞附近 <color=#ffffff>一階</color> 的 <color=#ffe14b>淤泥湧口</color> 。每4秒至多使用一次。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "3",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 能儲存的能量上限提升至 <color=#ffffff>4</color> 單位，並提升光照的亮度與範圍。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "4",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 能儲存的能量上限提升至 <color=#ffffff>6</color> 單位。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "5",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 能儲存的能量上限提升至 <color=#ffffff>7</color> 單位；\n<color=#ffe14b>純光綻放</color> 的冷卻時間降低至2秒。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "6",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>純光綻放</color> 將釋放更大的能量，能夠破壞 <color=#ffffff>二階</color> 的 <color=#ffe14b>淤泥湧口</color> 。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "7",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 能儲存的能量上限提升至 <color=#ffffff>9</color> 單位。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "8",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 能儲存的能量上限提升至 <color=#ffffff>10</color> 單位；\n<color=#ffe14b>純光綻放</color> 的影響範圍提升，並在使用時能夠尋找附近的"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 3831,
        "name": "流明晶石",
        "desc": "<p>湛藍如天幕的晶石，表面光芒明滅，似乎在呼應著地層深處不可見的高遠天空...<br>側耳細聽，彷彿能聽到其中傳來細微的嘆息。<br>說來奇怪，這塊晶石有一種溫暖的觸感。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/125391187/c61ace426856fcf41defec2fc476720f_4686018313795104572.png",
        "displayStyle": "text",
        "menuId": 9
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "9",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "裝備 <color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 時，使角色即使處於淤泥當中也能使用衝刺與替代衝刺的能力；\n使用 <color=#ffe14b>純光綻放</color> 後，將恢復體力。"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "10",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffe14b>流明石觸媒</color> 已經強化至等級上限。願這小小的光芒能為黑暗的旅途帶來些許慰藉。"
      },
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "level": 1,
        "text": "流明石觸媒用途",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/12/21/142453215/abbb279813cadcf1eb8157d33af71b30_5864624263074742632.gif",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "使用 <color=#ffe14b>純光綻放</color> 破壞不同階級的 <color=#ffe14b>淤泥湧口</color> 與其周邊的黑泥。\n在層岩巨淵·地下礦區提供光照。"
      },
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "level": 1,
        "text": "相關詞條與教學",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
